### AI List Generator Prompt #####
Create a grocery list for {prompt} under a total budget of ${budget}.
Please consider these dietary preferences: {userPrefs}.
Use ingredients available at Kroger stores near {storeLocation}.


### Recipe Generator Prompt ###
Suggest a recipe for a {mealType} that serves {servings} people.
The meal should be {dietaryPrefs} and cost under ${budget}.
Include a name, ingredients, and instructions. Prefer Kroger-sourced items.

### AI Insight Prompt ###
Review this grocery list: {itemList}.
Generate smart savings suggestions under $5 and show where substitutions can reduce cost.
Include healthier or budget alternatives where possible.


